		<text id="0" type="text/plain" rect="(111.0, 222.0, 333.0, 177.0)" font-family="Segoe UI" font-size="12">Who writes? Who are the top writers?

Import bssdh_metadata.csv
Use Data Table to inspect the data
Select Rows - author role is aut
Edit Domain - author -&gt; categorical
Group by author. Author - count
Data table - black high to low. Select top 25.
Bar plot. Value = author - Count. Annotation = author</text>
